Revision history for Tvh-Htsp-Client

0.06    23 June 2026
        - changed another German code comment to English
        - added three more error checks
        - added five more test cases
        - improved degug output for better readability
        - changed Error messages to itentify package plus method
        - return messages of type 4 'Binary blob' converted to hex string
        - debug output serialised messages converted to hex string
        - method 'getChanNamId' now also takes channel Number as parameter

0.05    10 June 2026
        - bumped minimum Perl version to 5.28 due to 'Tests are failing with perls < 5.28.0'

0.04    10 June 2026
        - no functional changes
        - changed German code comments to English
        - amended documentation
        - added __PACKAGE__ to Error messages to itentify their origin

0.03    18 July 2025
        - added 'htsmsg_deserialise' method

0.02    12 July 2025
        - added 'getChanUuidId' method

0.01    11 July 2025
        - Version 0.01 - initial release
